				<h1>The Party of Innovation</h1>
				
									<h2 id="deck">Copyright reform, looser licensing, and an agenda for a tech-savvy GOP</h2>
								
            	<div class="byline">
								
												  By <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.theamericanconservative.com/author/derek-khanna" title="View all posts by Derek Khanna">Derek Khanna</a></span> &bull; <a href="http://www.theamericanconservative.com/articles/the-party-of-innovation/" title="12:05 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">May 14, 2014</span></a>

									</div>
            
           
			
            
				<ul class="article-tools clearfix">
				  <li>
						<div class="fb-like" data-href="http://www.theamericanconservative.com/articles/the-party-of-innovation/" data-send="true" data-layout="button_count" data-width="125" data-show-faces="false" data-font="lucida grande"></div>
				  </li>
				  <li>
